desc: X Item '--input-mach=machine' Set the matching input ELF machine type to mach…
X Item '--output-mach=machine' Change the ELF machine type in the ELF header …
X Item '--input-type=type' Set the matching input ELF file type to type
X Item '--output-type=type' Change the ELF file type in the ELF header to type
X Item '--input-osabi=osabi' Set the matching input ELF file OSABI to osabi
X Item '--output-osabi=osabi' Change the ELF OSABI in the ELF header to osabi
X Item '--input-abiversion=version' Set the matching input ELF file ABIVERSIO…
X Item '--output-abiversion=version' Change the ELF ABIVERSION in the ELF hea…
X Item '--enable-x86-feature=feature' Set the feature bit in program property…
X Item '--disable-x86-feature=feature' Clear the feature bit in program prope…
X Item '--version' . PD Display the version number of elfedit
X Item '--help' . PD Display the command-line options understood by elfedit
